        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "How does wood rot happen in a desert city?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Repeated irrigation overspray, splash-back, and failed paint/caulk details can keep small areas wet enough to rot."
        }
